PrimeVul
--------
benchmarks/cpp_eval_real.jsonl is a filtered subset (C++ paired rows,
leakage-filtered against BigVul) of the PrimeVul dataset, obtained from the
Hugging Face mirror colin/PrimeVul at revision
4fd7158322872d711e90f091dbd8673ef32cb1be (mirror of the official
DLVulDet/PrimeVul release, https://github.com/DLVulDet/PrimeVul).

